as he does, apparently.

00:08:11.074 --> 00:08:14.828 position:50% align:center
[gasps] Then she's
gotta be over 5'7!

00:08:14.911 --> 00:08:16.413 position:50% align:center
[MIYANO]
So, there's hope.

00:08:16.496 --> 00:08:19.082 position:50% align:center
Maybe in a year I'll
grow to be that tall, too!

00:08:20.333 --> 00:08:23.378 position:50% align:center
